      Procedure.l SetItemText( *this._s_WIDGET, Item.l, Text.s, Column.l = 0 )
         Protected result
         
         If *this\type = #__type_Tree Or
            *this\type = #__type_ListIcon Or
            *this\type = #__type_Properties
            
